c-id=\"1\" data-awb-toc-options=\"{&quot;allowed_heading_tags&quot;:{&quot;h2&quot;:0,&quot;h3&quot;:1},&quot;ignore_headings&quot;:&quot;.awb-toc-el__list.awb-toc-el__list--0 li:first-child&quot;,&quot;ignore_headings_words&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;enable_cache&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;highlight_current_heading&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;hide_hidden_titles&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;limit_container&quot;:&quot;post_content&quot;,&quot;select_custom_headings&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-angle-right far&quot;,&quot;counter_type&quot;:&quot;custom_icon&quot;}\" style=\"--awb-item-font-size:var(--awb-typography4-font-size);--awb-item-line-height:var(--awb-typography4-line-height);--awb-item-letter-spacing:var(--awb-typography4-letter-spacing);--awb-item-text-transform:var(--awb-typography4-text-transform);--awb-item-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-item-color-hover:var(--awb-color5);--awb-item-bg-color-hover:rgba(101,189,125,0);--awb-counter-color:var(--awb-color6);--awb-hover-counter-color:var(--awb-color5);--awb-list-indent:15px;--awb-item-padding-top:3px;--awb-item-padding-right:0;--awb-item-padding-bottom:5px;--awb-item-padding-left:0;--awb-item-font-family:var(--awb-typography4-font-family);--awb-item-font-weight:var(--awb-typography4-font-weight);--awb-item-font-style:var(--awb-typography4-font-style);\"><div class=\"awb-toc-el__content\"></div></div>\n<div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-8 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">What Is the Avada Builder Library?</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-9\"><p>Think of the <a href=\"https://avada.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> Builder Library as your personal design vault inside Avada. It stores all your saved Page/Post Templates, Containers, Columns, <a href=\"https://avada.com/elements/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Design &amp; Layout Elements</a>, <a href=\"https://avada.com/documentation/how-to-use-post-cards-in-avada/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Post Cards</a>, and <a href=\"https://avada.com/feature/mega-menu-builder/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Mega Menus</a>basically, anything youve built and saved for reuse lives here. You can find the content in the <strong>WordPress Dashboard  Avada  Library</strong>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"--awb-liftup-border-radius:7px;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><div class=\"awb-image-frame awb-image-frame-4 imageframe-liftup imageframe-4\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--awb-color2);border-radius:7px;\"><a href=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard.png\" class=\"fusion-lightbox\" data-rel=\"iLightbox[6b34392d2fca0b1f5f8]\" data-title=\"Avada Builder Library Dashboard\" title=\"Avada Builder Library Dashboard\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2000\" height=\"973\" alt=\"Avada Builder Library Dashboard\" src=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard.png\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-897104\" srcset=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard-200x97.png 200w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard-400x195.png 400w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard-600x292.png 600w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard-800x389.png 800w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard-1200x584.png 1200w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/avada-builder-library-post-dashboard.png 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 2000px\" /></a></span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-10\"><p>Here, youll see a list of everything youve saved. Maybe you have some excellent layouts, custom sections, or reusable content blocks. And if youd like to use them on another Avada website, thats where importing and exporting come in.</p>\n<p>For a detailed overview of how to use the Avada Builder Library, please see this <a href=\"https://avada.com/blog/how-to-use-the-avada-builder-library/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">article</a>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-9 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:var(--awb-custom_color_1);--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color8);\">Exporting</mark> Avada Builder Library Content</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-video fusion-youtube\" style=\"--awb-max-width:1280px;--awb-max-height:720px;--awb-align-self:center;--awb-width:100%;\"><div class=\"video-shortcode\"><priv-fac-lite-youtube class=\"fusion-hidden lty-load\" data-privacy-type=\"youtube\" videoid=\"lWx3Eiwaybg\" class=\"landscape\" params=\"wmode=transparent&autoplay=1&amp;enablejsapi=1\" title=\"Avada Builder Library Import &amp; Export\" data-button-label=\"Play Video\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-thumbnail-size=\"auto\" data-no-cookie=\"on\"></priv-fac-lite-youtube><div class=\"fusion-privacy-placeholder\" style=\"width:1280px; height:720px;\" data-privacy-type=\"youtube\"><div class=\"fusion-privacy-placeholder-content\"><div class=\"fusion-privacy-label\">For privacy reasons YouTube needs your permission to be loaded.</div><button data-privacy-type=\"youtube\" class=\"fusion-button button-default fusion-button-default-size button fusion-privacy-consent\">I Accept</button></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-11\"><p>Lets start with the export process  thats how you get your saved designs out of one Avada website.</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-3 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p>From your <strong>Avada Dashboard</strong>, go to <strong>Options  Builder Options</strong>.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Scroll down until you find two sections:</div></li></ul><ul style=\"--awb-margin-left:35px;--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-4 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-from-left fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Export Library Content</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-from-left fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Export Templates</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-12\"><p>Heres what each one does:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-5 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">Export Library Content:</mark>  This exports everything in your Avada Builder Library except full-page templates. When you click this button, Avada will download an XML file to your computer.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">Export Templates:</mark>  This one exports your full-page templates and downloads them as an XML file.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-13\"><p>Now youve got your saved items exported  two neat little XML files on your computer, ready to be imported into another Avada site.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-10 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:var(--awb-custom_color_1);--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color8);\">Importing</mark> Library Content to Another Avada Site</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-14\"><p>Lets switch over to the new Avada site where you want your content to go.</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-6 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p>Navigate over to <strong>Avada  Library</strong>.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p>Next, go to <strong>Options  Builder Options.</strong></p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p>Scroll down to the <strong>Import Avada Builder Content</strong> section.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p>Click Choose File, select one of the <strong>XML</strong> files you exported, and then click <strong>Import</strong>.</p>\n</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-15\"><p>Youll get a <strong>Content successfully imported</strong> message once its done. Repeat the same process for the other <strong>XML</strong> file (the one with your templates or other saved items).</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-11 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">What Are The Benefits?</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-16\"><p>Importing/exporting <a href=\"https://avada.com/documentation/how-to-import-export-avada-builder-library-content/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Builder Library content</a> isnt just a neat trickits a real workflow booster. Here are the biggest wins for web designers using Avada and <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress</a>:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-custom_color_5);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-7 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><strong>Massive time savings</strong> &#8211; Build once, reuse everywhere. Port your hero sections, footers, pricing tables, and contact forms across projects instead of rebuilding from scratch.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><strong>Consistent branding across sites</strong> &#8211; Keep typography, spacing, color usage, and UI patterns identical by reusing the same containers, elements, and templates. Fewer almost matches, more polish.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><strong>Scales for agencies &amp; freelancers</strong> &#8211; Create a starter library (headers, CTAs, feature blocks) and deploy it to every new client site. It turns onboarding a new project into a head start.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><strong>Clean client hand-offs</strong> &#8211; Deliver a curated pack of approved sections/templates so clients can add new pages without breaking design standards.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><strong>Rapid prototyping &amp; A/B testing</strong> &#8211; Duplicate sections to new installs, test variations, and ship improvements back to your master library.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><strong>Team collaboration</strong> &#8211; Share the same building blocks across designers/devs. Everyone works from one source of truthno which version? confusion.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-12 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\">Practical Examples</h3></div><ul style=\"--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-8 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-ballot-check fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Launch a portfolio network: export your best case-study layout, import to each new site, swap contentdone.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-ite