_column fusion-builder-column-8 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:20px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-38\"><p>Streamlining how you manage form submissions can transform your websites efficiency. Collecting leads, support requests, or feedback becomes much faster when you move data from your inbox into an organized systemsaving you hours each week.</p>\n<p>To address these challenges, this integration helps streamline your process. We&#8217;ll show how connecting <a href=\"https://avada.com/feature/form-builder/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Forms</a> with <a href=\"https://workspace.google.com/intl/en_us/products/sheets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Google Sheets</a> simplifies your workflow, who benefits most, and how it only takes a few minutes to set up.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-35 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Overview</h2></div><div class=\"awb-toc-el awb-toc-el--3\" data-awb-toc-id=\"3\" data-awb-toc-options=\"{&quot;allowed_heading_tags&quot;:{&quot;h2&quot;:0,&quot;h3&quot;:1},&quot;ignore_headings&quot;:&quot;.awb-toc-el__list.awb-toc-el__list--0 li:first-child&quot;,&quot;ignore_headings_words&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;enable_cache&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;highlight_current_heading&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;hide_hidden_titles&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;limit_container&quot;:&quot;post_content&quot;,&quot;select_custom_headings&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;icon&quot;:&quot;fa-angle-right far&quot;,&quot;counter_type&quot;:&quot;custom_icon&quot;}\" style=\"--awb-item-font-size:var(--awb-typography4-font-size);--awb-item-line-height:var(--awb-typography4-line-height);--awb-item-letter-spacing:var(--awb-typography4-letter-spacing);--awb-item-text-transform:var(--awb-typography4-text-transform);--awb-item-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-item-color-hover:var(--awb-color5);--awb-item-bg-color-hover:rgba(101,189,125,0);--awb-counter-color:var(--awb-color6);--awb-hover-counter-color:var(--awb-color5);--awb-list-indent:15px;--awb-item-padding-top:3px;--awb-item-padding-right:0;--awb-item-padding-bottom:5px;--awb-item-padding-left:0;--awb-item-font-family:var(--awb-typography4-font-family);--awb-item-font-weight:var(--awb-typography4-font-weight);--awb-item-font-style:var(--awb-typography4-font-style);\"><div class=\"awb-toc-el__content\"></div></div>\n<div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-36 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Why Connect Avada Forms to Google Sheets?</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-39\"><p>Form Submission options control what happens when the form data is submitted. It can be a range of things, such as redirecting the user to a different URL, saving the form data to the database, forwarding the sender details to <a href=\"https://mailchimp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MailChimp</a> or <a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HubSpot</a> to add them to a mailing list, or even opening an <a href=\"https://avada.com/feature/off-canvas-builder/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Off-Canvas</a> asset.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-11 hover-type-none\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--awb-color3);\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1233\" alt=\"Google Sheets\" title=\"Google Sheets\" src=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal.png\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-896990\" srcset=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal-200x137.png 200w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal-400x274.png 400w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal-600x411.png 600w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal-800x548.png 800w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal-1200x822.png 1200w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-forms-google-sheets-post-internal.png 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1800px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-40\"><p>Every submission through your website form is a potential customer, a request, or valuable feedback. However, if those submissions stay trapped in your <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress</a> Dashboard or email inbox, it can be fairly difficult to track, share, or analyze them. By sending <a href=\"https://avada.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada</a> Form entries directly to a Google Sheet, you can:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-21 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-analytics fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Keep all form data in one central place  easy to search, filter, and organize.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-analytics fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Collaborate with your team in real time without logging in to your WordPress site.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-analytics fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Use Google Sheets as a lightweight CRM to assign statuses, add notes, and sort potential leads.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-analytics fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Connect your Google Sheets data to other tools such as <a href=\"https://zapier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zapier</a>, <a href=\"https://lookerstudio.google.com/navigation/reporting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Looker Studio</a>, or numerous automation workflows.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-analytics fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Analyze Google Sheets data using <a href=\"https://gemini.google.com/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gemini</a> to turn information into a conversational, AI-powered workspace  where you can explore and use your data without needing advanced spreadsheet skills.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-37 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Who Is This Integration For?</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-41\"><p>This setup is perfect for anyone who uses Avada Forms to gather information and wants a smarter way to manage it  including:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-22 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Small business owners</strong> who want an easy way to track inquiries and leads.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Marketing teams</strong> managing campaign sign-ups or newsletter opt-ins.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Support teams</strong> who want form submissions logged for faster response tracking.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Event organizers</strong> collect registrations, RSVPs, or volunteer signups.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-circle fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Freelancers and consultants</strong> who want to organize contact form submissions by project or client.</p>\n</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-38 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Real-World Examples</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-42\"><p>Lets say you run a <a href=\"https://avada.website/interior-design/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">interior design agency</a> and use Avadas contact form for new project inquiries. Instead of manually checking each submission, you connect your form to a Google Sheet. Now, every time someone fills out the form, their name, email, project type, and message appear instantly in your spreadsheet. With this information, one can:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-23 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Use <mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">conditional formatting</mark> to highlight high-priority projects.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Encourage <mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">team collaboration</mark> to improve efficiency and lead generation.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-long-arrow-alt-right fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">Track customer trends</mark> by filtering submissions based on predefined values.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-43\"><p>Its automated, organized, and effortless  no extra plugins or software required. Lets look at a few other ways this integration can be useful in everyday scenarios:</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-39 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\">Manage Lead Generation</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-44\"><p>An agency, for example, can send all Contact Us form submissions to Google Sheets. The team can then track leads, add follow-up notes, and share communication progress  all in one collaborative document.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-40 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\">Event Registrations</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-45\"><p>An event organizer can collect attendee sign-ups via Avada Forms and see registrations appear in real time on a shared sheet. Perfect for checking numbers and managing logistics on the go.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-41 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\">Customer Feedback</h3></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-46\"><p>Support or customer experience teams can collect feedback submissions and automatically organize them by rating or category, helping to identify trends quickly.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-42 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">How It Works (In Simple Terms)</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-47\"><p>Technically, this type of integration uses Google Apps Script (a built-in Google tool) as a bridge between your Avada Form and the Google Sheet.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-video fusion-youtube\" style=\"--awb-max-width:1280px;--awb-max-height:720px;--awb-align-self:center;--awb-width:100%;\"><div class=\"video-shortcode\"><priv-fac-lite-youtube class=\"fusion-hidden lty-load\" data-privacy-type=\"youtube\" videoid=\"B6S6kwLL1I4\" class=\"landscape\" params=\"wmode=transparent&autoplay=1&amp;enablejsapi=1\" title=\"Using Notifications in Avada Forms\" data-button-label=\"Play Video\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-thumbnail-size=\"auto\" data-no-cookie=\"on\"></priv-fac-lite-youtube><div class=\"fusion-privacy-placeholder\" style=\"width:1280px; height:720px;\" data-privacy-type=\"youtube\"><div class=\"fusion-privacy-placeholder-content\"><div class=\"fusion-privacy-label\">For privacy reasons YouTube needs your permission to be loaded.</div><button data-privacy-type=\"youtube\" class=\"fusion-button button-default fusion-button-default-size button fusion-privacy-consent\">I Accept</button></div></div></div></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-48\"><p>Once set up, whenever someone submits a form on your website, their data is automatically added as a new row in your spreadsheet.</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;--awb-circlecolor:var(--awb-color2);--awb-circle-yes-font-size:14.08px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-24 fusion-checklist-default type-numbered\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\">1</span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Create a new Google Sheet.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\">2</span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Add a short script (example provided <a href=\"https://avada.com/documentation/how-to-connect-avada-forms-with-google-sheets/#toc_Create_App\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>).</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\">3</span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Deploy the script as a web app.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-yes\">4</span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Add that web app URL to your forms submission settings in Avada.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"><div class=\"fusion-separator-border sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"--awb-height:20px;--awb-amount:20px;border-color:var(--awb-color3);border-top-width:0px;\"></div></div><div class=\"fusion-alert alert custom alert-custom fusion-alert-left awb-alert-inherit-link-color\" style=\"--awb-background-color:#fff6e4;--awb-accent-color:var(--awb-color8);--awb-border-size:0px;--awb-border-top-left-radius:8px;--awb-border-top-right-radius:8px;--awb-border-bottom-left-radius:8px;--awb-border-bottom-right-radius:8px;\" role=\"alert\"><div class=\"fusion-alert-content-wrapper\"><span class=\"fusion-alert-content\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">* Expert Tip:</mark>  If you want a full step-by-step walkthrough, weve covered everything in detail in our <a href=\"https://avada.com/documentation/how-to-connect-avada-forms-with-google-sheets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">documentation guide</a>  including code snippets and setup screenshots.</span></div></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-43 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Summary</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-49\"><p>The ability to send your Avada Form submissions straight to Google Sheets is one of those small, powerful tricks that can completely change how you manage your website data.</p>\n<p>Its perfect for anyone who wants an easy, reliable, and flexible way to work with form information  without needing complex integrations or paid add-ons.</p>\n<p>Start organizing your data smarter  and free up more time to focus on the people behind the forms.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4