div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-71 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">In Summary</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-105\"><p>Components provide a straightforward way to manage complex Element combinations on your pages. They allow you to:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:#4abfee;--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-71 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-double fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Edit the component itself to apply updates across every instance on your website.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-check-double fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">Choose your level of complexitykeep things simple or dive into the details.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-106\"><p>Whether youre just starting out or an advanced website builder, components offer a powerful new toolset for creating in Avada 8. In combination with <a href=\"https://avada.com/feature/avada-studio/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Avada Studio</a>, components offer a fantastic way for unique Elements without the headache.</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:30px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-72 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Avada AI</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-16 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1500\" height=\"550\" alt=\"Avada AI Logo\" title=\"Avada AI Logo\" src=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post.png\" class=\"img-responsive wp-image-896967\" srcset=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post-200x73.png 200w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post-400x147.png 400w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post-600x220.png 600w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post-800x293.png 800w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post-1200x440.png 1200w, https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/avada-ai-logo-post.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1500px\" /></span></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:20px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-107\"><p>Since announcing Avada AI, weve received a lot of great feedback and questions. Heres a closer look at some of the most common ones:</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:10px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-73 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.33;\">Feedback Responses</h3></div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:#4abfee;--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-72 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-comments fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>How will it be added?</strong> &#8211; Avada AI will be a paid subscription add-on for Avada. Its delivered as a plugin, so if AI isnt for you, you can skip the plugin and your Avada install remains unchanged.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-comments fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Is Avada AI slowing down Avada 8?</strong> &#8211; No. Avada 8 remains our top priority, and development continues there. Additionally, since Avada AI is built on the same framework, work on the AI plugin also benefits Avada 8. Were targeting a release for Avada AI before the end of December and will soon move into beta testing.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-comments fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Is AI replacing normal support?</strong> &#8211; Not at all. Avada AI wont replace our support team. Its not just a generic chatbot either. It utilizes up-to-date Avada documentation, FAQs, and your current installation context to enhance accuracy.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-comments fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Will it generate Avada Builder content?</strong> &#8211; This is something wed love to introduce, but not in version 1. We want to ensure the quality of the generated layouts before adding this.</p>\n</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-comments fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\">\n<p><strong>Will it generate images?</strong> &#8211; Yes. Both image generation and editing are currently included, with multiple models and styles to choose from.</p>\n</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom:50px;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-74 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\"><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:32;line-height:1.25;\">Current Features</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-slider-sc fusion-has-margin\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"><div class=\"fusion-flexslider-loading flexslider flexslider-hover-type-none\" data-slideshow_autoplay=\"0\" data-slideshow_smooth_height=\"1\" data-slideshow_speed=\"7000\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:100%;\"><ul class=\"slides\"><li class=\"video\"><div class=\"full-video\"><div class=\"fusion-video fusion-selfhosted-video\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><div class=\"video-wrapper\"><video playsinline=\"true\" width=\"100%\" style=\"object-fit: cover;\" autoplay=