e-size-four\"><h4 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:20;--minFontSize:20;line-height:1.42;\">Standard Image Generation</h4></div></div></li><li class=\"video\"><div class=\"full-video\"><div class=\"fusion-video fusion-selfhosted-video\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><div class=\"video-wrapper\"><video playsinline=\"true\" width=\"100%\" style=\"object-fit: cover;\" autoplay=\"true\" muted=\"true\" loop=\"true\" preload=\"auto\" controls=\"1\"><source src=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/image-generation-2.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">Sorry, your browser doesn&#039;t support embedded videos.</video></div></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-78 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\"><h4 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:20;--minFontSize:20;line-height:1.42;\">Artistic Image Generation</h4></div></div></li><li class=\"video\"><div class=\"full-video\"><div class=\"fusion-video fusion-selfhosted-video\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"><div class=\"video-wrapper\"><video playsinline=\"true\" width=\"100%\" style=\"object-fit: cover;\" autoplay=\"true\" muted=\"true\" loop=\"true\" preload=\"auto\" controls=\"1\"><source src=\"https://avada.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/image-editing-3.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">Sorry, your browser doesn&#039;t support embedded videos.</video></div></div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-79 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four\"><h4 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" style=\"margin:0;text-transform:capitalize;--fontSize:20;--minFontSize:20;line-height:1.42;\">Image Editing</h4></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep\" style=\"align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-108\"><p>Heres what Avada AI can already do:</p>\n</div><ul style=\"--awb-iconcolor:var(--awb-color8);--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;\" class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-73 fusion-checklist-default type-icons\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-badge-check fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">Ask</mark> &#8211; You can conduct conversations with the AI and save them for later reference. It has access to Avada documentation and FAQs, and when a response references docs, youll get direct links. Conversations maintain context, allowing you to ask follow-up questions. And youre not limited to supportyou can also ask about design, marketing, or content ideas.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-badge-check fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\"><mark class=\"fusion-highlight custom-textcolor highlight1 awb-highlight-background rounded\" style=\"--awb-color:#282828;--awb-text-color:var(--awb-color1);\">Write</mark> &#8211; You can generate new text to use in the Avada Builder, or edit existing text inline. Control the output with options like the number of variations, language, context, and whether to replace or append. Use it for everything from generating blog excerpts based on post content to refining your custom CSS.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\" style=\"\"><span class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-badge-check fal\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-